# Place trained model weights in this directory.
#
# Expected files (configured in configs/settings.yaml):
#   yolo_solar.pt        — YOLO panel detection weights
#   mobilenet_solar.pth  — Fine-tuned MobileNetV2 weights
#   xgboost_solar.joblib — Trained XGBoost pipeline
#
# This file is tracked by git to preserve the directory structure.
# The weight files themselves are NOT committed (add to .gitignore).
